matter when the human heart
can only find meaning

50:36.492 --> 50:38.949
in the smallest of moments?

50:40.496 --> 50:43.624
They’re here among us.

50:45.293 --> 50:49.536
In the shadows,
in the light. Everywhere.

50:52.425 --> 50:54.757
Do they even know yet?

51:08.316 --> 51:11.934
All right, I'm here.
Now what do you want?

51:14.697 --> 51:15.686
Peter?

51:22.747 --> 51:25.910
