51:31.339 --> 51:34.046
It's my turn to be somebody
now, Nathan!

51:34.634 --> 51:36.920
Come on, Peter,
quit screwing around!

52:19.721 --> 52:21.006
Peter!

52:21.097 --> 52:22.758
(BOTH GRUNTING)

52:27.895 --> 52:31.479
You're flying, Nathan.
You're flying.

52:32.233 --> 52:34.519
How did you...
I don't know.

52:38.865 --> 52:40.730
No! No!
